<p><strong>No action is required on your part to address this issue, and your domains have continued serving content as normal during this time. </strong>We are restoring any records that may have been mistakenly marked as unverified, and your domains will continue to serve content to users as normal.</p>


<p>We apologize for any inconvenience this may have caused.</p>


